OL,3,CFormer Nasa scientist defrauded
OL,4,Cinvestors and used money to buy house
OL,6,FAn 85-year-old former Nasa scientist
OL,7,Fdefrauded investors out of hundreds of
OL,8,Fthousands of pounds, and used some of
OL,9,Fthe money to buy a house.
OL,11,FJohn Burford generated more than #1
OL,12,Fmillion from 100 investors. But only
OL,13,F#760,000 was ever traded ` much of
OL,14,Fwhich was lost.
OL,16,FSubstantial amounts of the money
OL,17,Finvestors sent him was actually used
OL,18,Fto buy his own home, a court heard.
