OL,3,CFormer Nasa scientist defrauded
OL,4,Cinvestors and used money to buy house
OL,6,FBurford appeared at Westminster
OL,7,FMagistrates' Court on Friday wearing a
OL,8,Fbrown jacket, grey trousers and brown
OL,9,Fboots.
OL,11,FHe admitted fraud by false
OL,12,Frepresentation and carrying on a
OL,13,Fregulated activity when not authorised
OL,14,Fbetween January 2020 and December 2023.
OL,16,FHe has a PhD in physics from the
OL,17,FUniversity of Toronto and worked for
OL,18,FNasa in its manned Mars exploration
OL,19,Fteam based in Washington DC, before
OL,20,Fmoving into finance, his biography on
OL,21,Fpublisher Pan Macmillan's website says.
