OL,3,CFormer Nasa scientist defrauded
OL,4,Cinvestors and used money to buy house
OL,6,FProsecutor Tom Godfrey told the court
OL,7,FBurford set up a scheme which sent
OL,8,Fsubscribers daily email alerts with
OL,9,Finvestment opportunities.
OL,11,FHe traded #760,000 worth of the money
OL,12,Fgenerated, but "lost significant
OL,13,Fsums", Mr Godfrey said.
OL,15,F"He used substantial amounts of the
OL,16,Fmoney received to buy his own home,"
OL,17,Fhe added.
