OL,3,CFormer Nasa scientist defrauded
OL,4,Cinvestors and used money to buy house
OL,6,FThe former scientist, who now lives in
OL,7,FMansfield, Nottinghamshire, was the
OL,8,Fsole director of Financial Trading
OL,9,FStrategies Ltd, but was not authorised
OL,10,Fto trade in the UK, the court heard.
OL,12,FCarrying out unauthorised business is
OL,13,Fan offence punishable by a fine and/or
OL,14,Fup to two years' imprisonment.
OL,16,FBurford, who has no previous
OL,17,Fconvictions, will be sentenced at
OL,18,FSouthwark Crown Court at a later date.
